name: ABOUTUS
html:
With Almost Two Decades Of Experience, We Are Confident When We Say That We Are The Top Redmond Moving Company For Your Local Moving Needs

Established in 2003, Simple Move Redmond has been successfully helping residents, house owners, and business owners move their furniture and possessions locally, in Redmond WA. We offer moving solutions for any move, big or small, including; high-rise apartments; low-rise units, houses, offices, storages, etc.

We pride ourselves on offering a wide range of moving solutions at an affordable price and a service that is second-to-none in the industry. Simple Move Redmond offers the following moving solutions:

  • LOCAL MOVING REDMOND
  • RESIDENTIAL MOVING REDMOND
  • COMMERCIAL MOVING REDMOND
  • APARTMENT MOVING REDMOND
  • STORAGE IN AND OUT REDMOND
  • PACKING SERVICE REDMOND
  • PACKERS AND MOVERS REDMOND
  • LABOR-ONLY MOVING REDMOND
  • And much more!

We Are One Of The Top Movers In Seattle With Personalized Moving Solutions

You are in total control of your moving costs, and we are very flexible and can assist with as much or as little as you like.

Having more than 15 years’ experience in the moving business taught us many things. The first and most important is that keeping our customers should be our main goal. We just love making our customers happy and worry-free. We know that relocating is one of the most difficult tasks you will ever have and we always try to make it as simple as possible for you.

Licensed, Experienced And Professional

Our professional local packer and movers are licensed, experienced, and before everything else, always ready to give their best. So, if you are looking for movers with a truck, we are here for you! Call Simple Move Redmond for a free moving quote!

Who we are

Seattle Professional Movers is a licensed and insured Seattle, WA Mover, that is committed to client satisfaction with a 5 star rating. We work with both residential and commercial customers. Whether your move is across the street or in a different city in the area, we can organize and carry out your next move smoothly. Our trucks are always clean, and we use the right kind of dollies and equipment to make sure that all of your furniture and precious belongings are safe. At Seattle Professional Movers our main goal is to help take the stress out of your impending relocation.
